title: Grappler - 1.0.9 [Intel/KG]
description:
New in this version
Fixed crash when searching


Use Grappler to download music videos and more from anywhere on the web. Grappler integrates with iTunes to enable direct downloading from flash, html5, and many other formats of video directly into your library while converting it into the media format of your choice. Download videos into iTunes for future viewing on your iPod, iPhone, or iPad along with any many other mobile devices. Inline video previews make grappler an essential tool for the searching the web.
